{"tid":185153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(求解夢) 人生疑似第一次比鬼責","createTime":"2017-04-03T09:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T13:20:03.000Z","uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1950a0ad72d3888f0a4d3c2ac138272bd29b0bf8","tid":185153,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"話說我尋晚十二點半上床訓 後尾唔知係真實發生定係夢景 我見到有個黑影上左我張床度 我以為係我細佬黎 我問佢做咩事上黎我張床 之後佢冇反應 跟住我想起身 但我手手腳腳全身都郁唔到 <br />\n<br />\n之後我望真啲個黑影 佢唔係我細佬黎 但個影全黑 望唔到個樣 之後佢講左佢 ：比張床（定係比少少位）我訓<br />\n<br />\n冇耐之後我就醒左/郁得返 個心跳得勁快 我唔肯定係真實發生定係夢景 但就算係個夢都係第一人稱 即係望野個角度同我隻眼一樣<br />\n<br />\n想問到底係真實發生定係夢景黎？ 兩者點分？ 我係咪真係比鬼責？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957c57a5bfa35056f4ba116c7d7db6aabdbb6747","tid":185153,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50f95ce763fe647cc988118a83f4f83914b1913d","tid":185153,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"冇經驗，真係驚既咪搵師父睇下，唔係既就暫時當冇件事先"},{"pid":"ba7789e6d9b3110f506bacd5d99fe7cab0373576","tid":185153,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"05b8ffff5e0dddd8248b6fd0cee3e5618f6c62e2","tid":185153,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放心啦 有左第一次好快陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c19240b7a20a3ee0849ef59dd06fc9a88e3a9e03","tid":185153,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放心啦 有左第一次好快陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n屌你老未 加油埋Math啦 LS呢啲科好主觀 話唔定升到grade呢"},